WEBVTT

00:21.151 --> 00:23.849
"Such a man as Malcolm deserves
nothing short of death."

00:23.849 --> 00:26.113
Elijah's blatantly ordering
his men to kill you.

00:26.113 --> 00:28.028
Our sister mosque in Newark.

00:28.028 --> 00:29.420
Brother Clyde is who
you should speak with.

00:29.420 --> 00:31.814
You can be
a great asset for us,

00:31.814 --> 00:33.685
given all that you learned
about Malcolm.

00:33.685 --> 00:35.470
This is what the CIA
can do for us.

00:35.470 --> 00:36.949
This is where you get
your M-16s,

00:36.949 --> 00:38.342
direct government issue?

00:38.342 --> 00:40.040
But I'm sure Joe Colombo
won't have any problem

00:40.040 --> 00:41.693
with where these guns came from.

00:41.693 --> 00:45.697
We started out small,
but this is gonna be big.

00:45.697 --> 00:48.874
I want you to stay because
I think you can help me.

00:48.874 --> 00:51.051
- And I like you.
- You're crazy.

00:51.051 --> 00:53.792
Kinda be like my female
consigliere, you know?

00:53.792 --> 00:55.316
He thinks
you're cheating him.

00:55.316 --> 00:57.535
His cut last month
was $2 million!

00:57.535 --> 01:00.669
He's never made that much
off heroin! That's a fact!

01:00.669 --> 01:02.497
Part of the reason
for the hit

01:02.497 --> 01:04.629
was he thought I was fuckin'
his daughter, which I wasn't.

01:04.629 --> 01:07.371
But the other part
is that he thinks

01:07.371 --> 01:10.853
the dope puts me in position
to take over his territory.

01:10.853 --> 01:14.987
So I'm gonna prove him right.
I'm takin' Harlem.

01:14.987 --> 01:16.728
I should've smelled a rat
sooner myself.

01:16.728 --> 01:18.034
What?

01:18.034 --> 01:19.644
You were the only one I told

01:19.644 --> 01:22.386
about Malcolm speaking with Che
at the United Nations.

01:22.386 --> 01:24.997
I'm sorry, brother.
I don't trust you anymore.

01:24.997 --> 01:27.304
This partnership is over.

01:27.304 --> 01:30.699
I want your protection dismissed.

01:30.699 --> 01:32.875
You're not going anywhere.
Don't make me do it.

01:35.399 --> 01:38.402
<i>It seems your precautions
were unnecessary after all.</i>

01:38.402 --> 01:41.101
I suggest you take your men
and leave. For good.

01:46.932 --> 01:48.586
Drink?

01:48.586 --> 01:50.153
Mezzacorona?

01:50.153 --> 01:52.416
What's the occasion?

01:52.416 --> 01:55.115
Our most profitable
month yet.

01:55.115 --> 01:59.206
Which brings me to
our first order of business.

01:59.206 --> 02:01.338
I'm able to leverage
the Corsicans

02:01.338 --> 02:05.255
for three times as much dope
in the next shipment.

02:05.255 --> 02:06.778
Good, good.

02:06.778 --> 02:09.781
That'll make it
the largest in history.

02:09.781 --> 02:11.696
Yeah, if we all agree.

02:11.696 --> 02:14.699
Bravo. Bravo.

02:14.699 --> 02:17.137
But it comes
with a requirement.

02:18.660 --> 02:21.619
I want Chin Gigante out.

02:28.104 --> 02:32.587
Young man,
there's a <i>lot</i> to consider.

02:32.587 --> 02:36.112
Chin's the boss
of the most powerful borgata--

02:36.112 --> 02:39.637
He tried to fuckin' whack me, Carlo.

02:39.637 --> 02:47.776
I'm willing to forgive
and forget this, once.

02:47.776 --> 02:50.387
He'll still get his piece,

02:50.387 --> 02:54.217
but he's backseat
on the next shipment.

02:54.217 --> 02:57.481
I need the Commission to give me
full authority over Harlem

02:57.481 --> 03:01.006
for the purposes
of distributing the narcotics.

03:02.704 --> 03:04.923
All in favor?

03:21.810 --> 03:23.203
Yes.

03:23.203 --> 03:26.031
That's good.

03:26.031 --> 03:30.471
Alright, here's to a new ship,
and smooth sailing.

03:30.471 --> 03:31.515
<i>Salut.</i>

03:31.515 --> 03:33.474
<i>- Cin don.
- Salut.</i>

03:33.474 --> 03:35.215
<i>Buona fortuna.</i>

03:39.088 --> 03:41.786
Get up. Let's go.

03:41.786 --> 03:43.701
Get up.

03:43.701 --> 03:45.834
Today's your lucky day.

03:51.143 --> 03:53.363
There you are, my honey.
I love you.

03:53.363 --> 03:55.147
Oh, there he is.

03:55.147 --> 03:57.149
Oh, my honey.
Look at you!

03:57.149 --> 03:59.064
Oh, my God.

03:59.064 --> 04:00.240
Here you are!

04:00.240 --> 04:02.329
Mwah!
My baby!

04:02.329 --> 04:03.895
Look at you!

04:03.895 --> 04:05.288
You're free at last.

04:05.288 --> 04:07.334
This is the happiest day
of my life!

04:07.334 --> 04:08.552
He's home!

04:08.552 --> 04:10.728
And here you are!

